	</font>

186
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:44,240
<font color=#ffffff>
	Karamell, da drin ist er so gut wie
	</font>
<font color=#ffffff>
	nichts.
	</font>

187
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:47,200
<font color=#ffffff>
